# Flappy Bird Clone - Java Swing 🎮

A desktop-based Flappy Bird clone built using Java and Swing, designed to replicate the original game's mechanics and feel.

## 🛠️ Features

- Smooth animations using Java's game loop logic
- Obstacle (pipe) generation with increasing difficulty
- Collision detection for game-over conditions
- Score tracking and display
- Simple and intuitive keyboard controls

## 🧑‍💻 Technologies Used

- Java
- Java Swing (for GUI)
- Object-Oriented Programming (OOP)
